item.title: Nobodey can logg on to my server and i do have the ports open
item.dc:creator: @Java_Is_My_Bitch Java Is My Bitch™
item.description:
@Java_Is_My_Bitch wrote:

Maybe your router ip Has changed? Check it by double-clicking the two small computers in your task bar. Then click the support tab and look at the ip address, you will only be concerned with the last digits. Then if it has changed, make the changes to your portforwarding. And you will be able to log on.

Also to log onto your server, you can leave the Ip part blank, it will log in.
